    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>És melmelada: vet aquí el que és.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>It's jam--that's what it is.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Us he dit quaranta vegades que si no deixaveu la melmelada tranquila us llevaria la pell.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Forty times I've said if you didn't let that jam alone I'd skin you.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
