    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>I li fou cosa afalagadora, de reflexionar que ella havia descobert que la camisa era seca, sense que ningú s'adonés que aixo era la cosa que portava al magí.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>And it flattered her to reflect that she had discovered that the shirt was dry without anybody knowing that that was what she had in her mind.</seg></tuv>
