    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Jeff Thatcher immediatament avança a mostrar-se familiar amb el gran home i a ésser envejat per l'escola.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Jeff Thatcher immediately went forward, to be familiar with the great man and be envied by the school.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Hauria estat música per a son esperit, de sentir els murmuris.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>It would have been music to his soul to hear the whisperings:</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Mira-te'l, Jim! com puja allí damunt.</seg></tuv>
