    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Aquest procediment reeixí, i Tom comença sos gemecs altra vegada.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>This course worked well, and Tom began to groan again.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Sid badalla, s'estira, després s'aixeca damunt el colze amb un esbufec, i es posa a mirar Tom de fit a fit.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Sid yawned, stretched, then brought himself up on his elbow with a snort, and began to stare at Tom.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Tom seguí gemegant.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Tom went on groaning. Sid said:</seg></tuv>
