      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Tom was suffering in reality, now, so handsomely was his imagination working, and so his groans had gathered quite a genuine tone.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Sid corregué escales avall i digué: -Oh!</seg></tuv>
