    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Ah! Ja no voleu, ja no voleu?</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"Oh, you don't, don't you?</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>De manera que tot aquest terrabastall era perque us pensaveu romandre a casa, i fer campana, i anar a pescar?</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>So all this row was because you thought you'd get to stay home from school and go a-fishing?</seg></tuv>
