      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>She thrust it away again, but with less animosity. Tom patiently returned it to its place.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Tom escritoteja a la seva pissarra: «Preneu-lo, si us plau; en tinc més».</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Then she let it remain. Tom scrawled on his slate, "Please take it--I got more."</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>La noia pega llambregada a aquelles paraules, pero no féu cap senyal.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>The girl glanced at the words, but made no sign.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Aleshores el noi comença a dibuixar alguna cosa a la pissarra, tot amagant la seva obra amb la ma esquerra.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Now the boy began to draw something on the slate, hiding his work with his left hand.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Per algun temps la noia refusa de pendre'n coneixement; pero la seva humana curiositat no triga a manifestar-se per indicis tot just perceptibles: El minyó seguia treballant, aparentment, sense dar-se'n compte.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>For a time the girl refused to notice; but her human curiosity presently began to manifest itself by hardly perceptible signs.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>La noia féu una mena d'intent que no la comprometés, per a veure-ho; pero el minyó no revela que en tingués esment.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>The girl made a sort of non-committal attempt to see, but the boy did not betray that he was aware of it.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>A la fi ella va caure, i murmura amb certa vacil·lació: -Deixeu-m'ho veure.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>At last she gave in and hesitatingly whispered: "Let me see it."</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Tom descobrí en part una trista caricatura d'una casa, amb una teulada de dues pendents i un tirabuixó de fum que sortia de la xemeneia.</seg></tuv>
