    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Quan fou acabada, la contempla un moment i després zumzeja:</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>When it was finished, she gazed a moment, then whispered:</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Que és bonic! Feu un home.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"It's nice--make a man."</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
