    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Aleshores Tom comença d'escritotejar quelcom damunt la pissarra, tot amagant les paraules a la noia; pero ella no es retreia, aquesta vegada, i demana de veure-ho.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Now Tom began to scrawl something on the slate, hiding the words from the girl. But she was not backward this time.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Oh! No és res.</seg></tuv>
