    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Ara el seu esdevenidor se li mostrava tot franc al seu davant, i aureolat d'una resplendor inimaginable.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>That was it! _now_ his future lay plain before him, and glowing with unimaginable splendor.</seg></tuv>
