    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Hi posa la ma, i pronuncia aquests mots d'encantament, d'una manera impressionant: -Que allo que no hagi vingut aquí, se n'hi vingui!</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>He put his hand there and uttered this incantation impressively: "What hasn't come here, come!</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
