      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Huck mira amb el cor ple de joia.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"Well, he has, by jingoes!</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Oida, vatua!</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Did he before?"</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Que ho havia fet abans?</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"Yes, he did.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Sí, que ho havia fet; pero jo, com un ximple, no hi havia parat esment.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>But I, like a fool, never thought.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Aixo és de primera! sabeu? I ara per quí deu venir?</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Oh, this is bully, you know. _Now_ who can he mean?"</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>L'udol cessa.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>The howling stopped.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Tom es caragola les orelles.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Tom pricked up his ears.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Que és aixo?- zumzeja.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>What's that?" he whispered.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Sona com… com porcs que remuguin.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"Sounds like--like hogs grunting.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
