      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>When they had got to within five steps of the snorer, Tom stepped on a stick, and it broke with a sharp snap.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>L'home gemega, es retorcé una mica, i sa cara resta sota la llum de la lluna.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>The man moaned, writhed a little, and his face came into the moonlight.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Era Muff Potter.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>It was Muff Potter.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Els cors dels minyons havien romas aturats, i llurs cossos també, mentre l'home es movia; pero ara llurs temences s'esvairen.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>The boys' hearts had stood still, and their hopes too, when the man moved, but their fears passed away now.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
