    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Es giraren i veieren el gos singular que romania a tret d'on jeia Potter, encarant-se amb Potter, tot assenyalant el cel amb el nas. -Oh!</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>They turned and saw the strange dog standing within a few feet of where Potter was lying, and _facing_ Potter, with his nose pointing heavenward.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Manoi! Ve per ell!- exclamaren els dos nois, fent un bisbe.</seg></tuv>
