    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-I després… i després… Bé, no n'estic cert, pero em sembla com si haguéssiu manat a Sid que se n'anes i…i…i… -I que?</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"And then--and then--well I won't be certain, but it seems like as if you made Sid go and--and--" "Well?</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>I que?</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Well?</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Que li vaig fer fer, Tom?</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>What did I make him do, Tom?</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
