    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Vostre Honor: En les nostres observacions fetes a l'inici d'aquesta causa, prefigurarem el nostre proposit de demostrar que el nostre client realitza aquesta feta paorosa trobant-se sota la influencia d'un orb, irresponsable deliri produit per la beguda.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"Your honor, in our remarks at the opening of this trial, we foreshadowed our purpose to prove that our client did this fearful deed while under the influence of a blind and irresponsible delirium produced by drink.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Hem canviat de parer; la nostra defensa sera una altra.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>We have changed our mind. We shall not offer that plea."</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>I, adreçant-se al dependent: -Féu venir Tomas Sawyer.</seg></tuv>
