      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"Behind the elms that's on the edge of the grave."</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Joe l'Indi féu un moviment gairebé imperceptible.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Injun Joe gave a barely perceptible start.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
