      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Compreneu?, sabíem ben bé on havíem d'aferrar-los, per la vostra descripció: així és que ens esquitllarem de puntetes fins que n'arribarem a quinze peus (era negre com un celler, aquell caminal de roldó!), i aleshores m'adono que estava a punt d'esternudar.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>You see we knew right where to put our hands on them, by your description; so we crept along on tiptoe till we got within fifteen feet of them--dark as a cellar that sumach path was--and just then I found I was going to sneeze.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Quína mena de sort tan roina!</seg></tuv>
