      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>In a lucid interval, Huck feebly led up to the subject of taverns, and finally asked--dimly dreading the worst--if anything had been discovered at the Temperance Tavern since he had been ill.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>-Sí- digué la vídua.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>"Yes," said the widow.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Huck pega un bot en el seu llit, amb els ulls esverats. -Que!</seg></tuv>
