      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Tom said that they must have been missed long ago, and no doubt the search was going on.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Cridaria, i potser vindria algú.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>He would shout and maybe some one would come.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Ho intenta; pero, en la fosca, els ecos sonaven tan paorosament, que no va tornar-hi.</seg></tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>He tried it; but in the darkness the distant echoes sounded so hideously that he tried it no more.</seg></tuv>
