      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>But Becky was very weak.</seg></tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="ca"><seg>Digué que esperaria on es trobava, i moriria: poc havia de trigar gaire estona.</seg></tuv>
